Maintainer: Tobias Mildenberger <tobm@dtu.dk>
Description: A movement model that allows estimation of habitat preferences
    and fine-scale movement rates using various types of tagging data. It supports
    flexible spatiotemporal modeling with options for Kalman filter or matrix
    exponential approaches, and includes tools for data preparation, model
    fitting, and visualization.
